[gd_scene load_steps=112 format=3]

; BOWSER - DARK FORTRESS. Full castle-keep boss level: approach bridge
; over a lava chasm → gatehouse with arched gateway and flanking towers
; → courtyard with gallows & lava fountain → main keep (3 floors +
; throne hall + roof spire) → dungeon beneath → torture chamber.
; Palette: basalt + stone_dark + lava + fabric_red + gold + ember.
; ~75 subresources, 16 enemies (2 boss chain chomps, 3rd chain chomp
; guardian, 10 bobomb army, 2 piranha throne guards, 3 goomba, 2 koopa,
; 2 cuttlefish ravens), 30 yellow + 8 red coins, 1 star behind throne,
; 2 one-ups, metal cap in lava. CSG used for: gatehouse arch + doors,
; murder-hole slit, window-slits in towers, throne-hall rib vaults,
; spiral-stair cutouts, dungeon trapdoor opening, prison-cell bars,
; torture-chamber cage, observation-room wide windows.

